      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so pointless. i look at the sun coming up and i just think... why? why does another day even need to happen? it's just more time to feel this emptiness. it's like i'm just waiting for a pain that never stops. why is it so hard for people to just accept that sometimes, things are just broken beyond repair? sometimes it feels like the only way to stop the weight is to just... stop everything.",
